legacy_data/reports/

# Local working planning doc (never commit)
/PLANNING.md

# Retired freestyle planning surfaces (local historical and working records
# only). One root file carries both retired lineages: the freestyle
# reconciliation/remediation report and the Freestyle Closure Plan that
# replaced it in place at the same path. The single tracked authority for
# active freestyle work is the maintainers' private tracker.
/freestyle_remediation_report.md

